I agree with you, however, that role-play is not a valid excuse for for impinging on another's playing experience.<br>
<br>
6. I play on several different servers, with different rule-sets. One thing which I have learned, and which you evidently have not, is that &quot;EverQuest Etiquette&quot; varies from place to place and person to person.<br>
