y higher levels to get a feel for what this world is like, rather than telling us what you think it should be.  No one person wrote a set of rules for the people here, but one seems to be evolving nonetheless.  So in trying to buck against it, you are basicly fighting against an unspoken concensus of the whole community.<br>
